<t24help>
<header>
<product>EB</product>
<table>EB.SIGNATORY.GROUP</table>
</header>
<overview>
<ovdesc>

            <p>EB.SIGNATORY.GROUP is aimed at creating signatory groups.</p>
            <p />
            <p>    This table will contain the internal organisation</p>
            <p> structure of a corporate customer. Various groups of employees</p>
            <p> (To be stored as T24 customers) of the corporate organization</p>
            <p> will be grouped together as an identifiable group. The same group</p>
            <p> can be linked to the mandate such that appropriate rights can be provided.</p>
        </ovdesc>
<ovimage></ovimage>
</overview>
<menu>
<t>
<field>SIG.GROUP.ID</field>
<desc>
            <p>A Valid T24 Customer followed by a Static Text. Static text will always be converted to uppercase.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>START.DATE</field>
<desc>
            <p>Date from which this signatory customer is valid.</p>
            <p />
            <p> A valid date which cannot be backdated.</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>
                    <p>Validation Rules:</p>:</p>
            </p>
            <p>  1.Mandatory.</p>
            <p>  2. Date field</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>SIGNATORY.CUSTOMER</field>
<desc>
            <p>A valid  T24 CUSTOMER.</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>
                    <p>Validation Rules:</p>:</p>
            </p>
            <p>  1.Mandatory.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>DESCRIPTION</field>
<desc>
            <p>Description of the signatory group.</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>
                    <p>Validation Rules:</p>:</p>
            </p>
            <p>  1. Multi value language field.</p>
            <p>  2. Mandatory.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
<t>
<field>END.DATE</field>
<desc>
            <p>Date till which this signatory customer is valid.</p>
            <p />
            <p> A valid date which cannot be less than START.DATE .</p>
            <p />
            <p>
                <p>
                    <p>Validation Rules:</p>:</p>
            </p>
            <p>  1.Mandatory.</p>
            <p>  2.Date field.</p>
        </desc>
</t>
